1. Create a user controller with rspec.

    bundle exec rails g controller user


2. make the user a resource in config/routes.rb
   
   resources :users


3. View this in rake routes

   bundle exec rake routes


4. Write some tests 

4.1 for the user model

4.2 for the user controller


5. Create the index action and view.


6. Secure the user with Devise

   